aVYou may discover, as I did,
p157
aVthat a lot of things that you used to think were your fault,
p158
aVa lot of things you used to think about yourself,
p159
aVreally had nothing to do with you.
p160
aVIt wasn't your fault; you're just fine.
p161
aVAnd you're able to go back and forgive them.
p162
